open_text: The trainer explained concepts very clearly and was always available for doubts. The pace of training is good and I'm learning a lot about Java fundamentals.
Having issues with laptop performance and network connectivity. It's affecting my ability to follow along with coding exercises. Need better hardware support.
My mentor is fantastic! Always responds quickly to my questions and provides detailed explanations. The trainer makes complex topics easy to understand.
The curriculum is comprehensive but sometimes feels overwhelming. Would appreciate more hands-on practice sessions before assessments.
Batch owner is very supportive and regularly checks on our progress. The overall learning environment is positive and encouraging.
Frequent system crashes during virtual sessions. Trainer is good but technical issues are hampering the learning experience.
Mentor provides excellent guidance on projects. The training content is well-structured and covers all necessary topics for a beginner.
Outstanding trainer! Makes learning fun and interactive. I look forward to every session. Great use of real-world examples.
Major connectivity issues throughout the week. Batch owner seems overwhelmed and not very responsive to technical concerns.
Course material is good but could use more practical examples. Mentor is helpful but sometimes takes time to respond.
Trainer has excellent communication skills and creates an engaging learning atmosphere. Enjoying the interactive coding sessions.
Assessments are too frequent and stressful. Need more time to practice and understand concepts before being tested.
Mentor is very knowledgeable and patient. Lab setup is good and software tools are working well for most exercises.
Excellent trainer who goes above and beyond to help students. Batch owner is also very approachable and supportive.
Good learning environment but would like more group activities and peer collaboration opportunities in the curriculum.
Network issues persist and it's frustrating. Mentor tries to help but technical problems are beyond their control.
Trainer provides clear explanations and good feedback on assignments. Assessment format is fair and tests understanding well.
Love the hands-on approach to learning! The projects are challenging but achievable. Great balance of theory and practice.
Batch owner is organized but could communicate expectations more clearly. Mentor is supportive and provides good technical guidance.
Severe technical issues with development environment setup. Trainer is patient but we're losing valuable learning time due to tech problems.
Mentor creates a comfortable learning environment where I feel safe to ask questions. Peer interactions are also very positive.
Content is comprehensive but delivery could be more engaging. Trainer knows the subject well but presentation style could improve.
Assessment pressure is high and batch owner doesn't seem to understand the stress levels. Need better support during exam periods.
Trainer is excellent at explaining complex concepts simply. Lab infrastructure is mostly reliable with occasional minor issues.
Amazing learning experience! Mentor and trainer work well together to create a supportive and challenging environment.
Curriculum seems outdated and technical setup is problematic. Need modernized content and better technical support.
Both trainer and mentor are very supportive. They work as a team to ensure we understand concepts thoroughly before moving forward.
Batch owner is well-intentioned but could be more proactive in addressing group concerns. Overall atmosphere is positive though.
Assessments are poorly designed and don't reflect what we've learned. Training material doesn't align well with evaluation criteria.
Technical setup works most of the time. Would appreciate more interactive sessions and group projects to enhance engagement.
